metadata.name: SkyNet
metadata.description:
Enter the world of SkyNet, a cryptocurrency inspired by the unexplained mysteries of the skies. From fleets of silent drones to unidentified aerial phenomena (UAPs), the enigma of advanced technology hovering above us fuels both curiosity and speculation.

$DRONES symbolizes our quest to explore these mysteries and push the boundaries of what we know. Are they experimental human tech, advanced surveillance systems, or something beyond imagination? SkyNet is a community-driven movement to decode these shadows of the sky and uncover the truth.

Join the network: Unite with fellow explorers, share insights, and invest in the next wave of aerial intrigue and innovation. The truth is out thereâ€”be part of the revolution.
